time for a brand new #drawthisinyourstyle !!🍡
comment a flower if you’re thinking about joining!🌻🌷🌺

rules:

node.text:
here’s an artist support!🎨✨
guidelines:
🌱introduce yourself in the comments and tag some friends💫💘
🌸check out other artists in the comments to make new friends/mutuals! c:
🍡shares are appreciated so we can spread the support! (optional)
🌱have fun!! i’ll feature artists in my stories. if you’d like a story shoutout use the tag #cie_feature on your post 😤
.
i’ll go first!🌸hi everyone, i’m acatcie and i love drawing anime art✨my favorite artists are @kumozaian @fresh_bobatae and @ivyuun !
.
also, this post is sponsored by @huiontablet and they are providing three drawing tablets to support the art community! swipe to see the tablets :^) (the prizes are an inspiroy h420x, inspiroy h580x, and inspiroy h610x) ✨✨
if you’re interested in a tablet here are the guidelines:
1. follow @huiontablet 
2. participate in the artist support!🌊 (leave at least one comment)
.
there will be 3 winners in total, the winners will be chosen at random and @huiontablet will cover all the shipping fees!
.
if you’ve read up to this far i hope you have a great day and ty for all your support!!💖
.
.
.
#artistsupport #artistsupportartists #doodleart #animeart #aestheticart #mangaart

node.text:
🎨huion kamvas 16 (2021) review🎨
a big thanks to @huiontablet @huioncanada for sending me this tablet and giving me the opportunity to review it! if you’d like to know more about the product, check out the link in my highlights!🌸
overall i really really like this tablet; it runs smoothly and responsively and the shortcut buttons help a lot with my drawing process! the pen pressure is great and this tablet is really comfortable and fun to use! for anyone looking into digital art or in need of a tablet, i definitely recommend the huion kamvas 16 (2021)🌱
thank you so much @huioncanada @huiontablet for being patient with me for this collaboration!💞
.
also, this drawing idea was inspired by @yomuuiii ✨
.
.
.
#huion #huioncanada #digitalartist #aestheticart #artoninstagram
